OL,3,CMan, 77, airlifted to hospital after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by car that drove away
OL,6,FA 77-year-old man has been airlifted
OL,7,Fto hospital with significant injuries
OL,8,Fafter a car failed to stop in this
OL,9,Fmorning (Saturday, 1st June).
OL,11,FHe is in a stable condition.
OL,13,FAt 08:22 were called to report that a
OL,14,Fmale pedestrian had been struck on
OL,15,FKingsley Avenue.
OL,17,FThe vehicle, which was reported as
OL,18,Fbeing a silver-coloured car, initially
OL,19,Fstopped but then made off from the
OL,20,Fscene.
