OL,3,CMan, 77, airlifted to hospital after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by car that drove away
OL,6,FThe emergency services were called and
OL,7,Fthe pedestrian was airlifted to
OL,8,Fhospital in Stoke by the Air Ambulance.
OL,10,FOfficers later found the vehicle, a
OL,11,Fsilver Ford Focus, parked outside a
OL,12,Fproperty on Marsh Road.
OL,14,FThree men and a woman, who were inside
OL,15,Fthe property have been arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of driving offences. All
OL,17,Ffour remain in police custody.
