OL,3,CMan, 77, airlifted to hospital after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by car that drove away
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Andy Gibson
OL,7,Fsaid "the pedestrian is in a stable
OL,8,Fcondition however he has sustained
OL,9,Fsignificant injuries.
OL,11,F"I am urging anybody who may have
OL,12,Fwitnessed the collision, or anybody
OL,13,Fwho may have been in the vicinity of
OL,14,FKingsley Avenue this morning to
OL,15,Fcontact us as soon as possible. This
OL,16,Fincludes anybody who may have dash cam
OL,17,For CCTV footage.
